options.text: Can I journey on this ship?
Does Karamja have unusual customs then?

5ad83c7d-50b8-4578-942c-830bd31b4141.title: <player>
5ad83c7d-50b8-4578-942c-830bd31b4141.text: Can I journey on this ship?

3b095683-46ea-4eb5-8d2e-a232e877ccd4.title: Customs Officer
3b095683-46ea-4eb5-8d2e-a232e877ccd4.text: You need to be searched before you can board.

options.text: Search away, I have nothing to hide.
You're not putting your hands on my things!

2ce60787-0ffb-445a-951e-c3bed6437671.title: Customs Officer
2ce60787-0ffb-445a-951e-c3bed6437671.text:
Because Asgarnia has banned the import of intoxicating
spirits.

options.text: Search away, I have nothing to hide.
You're not putting your hands on my things!

8f21b334-6415-4680-a0b2-ee3a3880846e.title: <player>
8f21b334-6415-4680-a0b2-ee3a3880846e.text: Search away, I have nothing to hide.

f5c97b60-83bc-4a1e-9569-02befa692f78.title: Customs Officer
f5c97b60-83bc-4a1e-9569-02befa692f78.text: Aha, trying to smuggle rum are we?

05126fa4-20c4-4c76-adb5-ed8ebdab2468.title: Customs Officer
05126fa4-20c4-4c76-adb5-ed8ebdab2468.text:
Well you've got some odd stuff, but it's all legal. Now
you need to pay a boarding charge of 30 coins.

806ccaf5-5cb1-4901-b4ff-5d53e0180f59.title: <player>
806ccaf5-5cb1-4901-b4ff-5d53e0180f59.text: You're not putting your hands on my things!

24d4187d-ce95-4a1b-a95d-5a92a39776c2.title: Customs Officer
24d4187d-ce95-4a1b-a95d-5a92a39776c2.text: You're not getting on this ship then.

02595da0-9eb7-446f-8f2a-b28cfee5a3ea.title: <player>
02595da0-9eb7-446f-8f2a-b28cfee5a3ea.text: Does Karamja have any unusual customs then?

91aef841-a390-482c-a81a-68a261b363b5.title: Customs Officer
91aef841-a390-482c-a81a-68a261b363b5.text: I'm not that sort of customs officer.

args: The customs officer confiscates your rum.
You will need to find some way to smuggle it off the island...
